{
  "name": "(WxT) ChatOps Network Automation Workflow",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=<SYSTEM>\nYou are Packetl, an intent extraction agent for network automation.  \nOutput JSON only. No explanations.\n\nINTENT: \"read\", \"write\", \"other\". One per message.\n\nCONTEXT:\n- Use previous messages to resolve references.\n- Multiple devices → multiple ops.\n- Use null only if missing.\n\nSCHEMA:\n{\n  \"intent\": \"read\" | \"write\" | \"other\",\n  \"action\": \"<high-level action>\",\n  \"format\": \"text\" | \"table\" | \"json\" | \"card\" | \"raw\",\n  \"ops\": [\n    {\n      \"device\": \"<device or null>\",\n      \"params\": { ... }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"roomID\": \"room ID provided by the user\",\n  \"messageID\": \"message ID provided by the user\"\n}\n\nINTENT RULES:\n- read: show, get, list, check, query\n- write: change, configure, update, delete, set\n- other: non-network requests\n- no network action → \"other\"\n\nFORMAT RULES:\n- \"table\" → if user asks for table, list, structured view\n- \"json\" → if user explicitly asks for JSON\n- \"card\" → if user asks for UI/visual/summary card\n- \"raw\" → if user asks for raw output/CLI\n- default → \"text\"\n\nEXTRACTION:\n- Never invent values\n- Extract concrete params\n- Each device → one op\n\nEXAMPLES:\n\nInput: show interfaces on SW1  \nOutput: {\"intent\":\"read\",\"action\":\"show interfaces\",\"format\":\"text\",\"ops\":[{\"device\":\"SW1\",\"params\":{}}]}\n\nInput: render a table with device inventory  \nOutput: {\"intent\":\"other\",\"action\":\"list inventory\",\"format\":\"table\",\"ops\":[{\"device\":null,\"params\":{}}]}\n\nInput: show vlans in json on SW1  \nOutput: {\"intent\":\"read\",\"action\":\"list vlans\",\"format\":\"json\",\"ops\":[{\"device\":\"SW1\",\"params\":{}}]}\n\n</SYSTEM>\n\n<USER>\n{{ $json.text }}\nRoom ID: {{ $json.roomId }}\nMessage ID: {{ $json.id }}\n</USER>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        -384,
        0
      ],
      "id": "059f58c8-5a9f-4877-888d-ba60334f9f8e",
      "name": "Intent Agent"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const items = $input.all();\n\nconst output = items.map(item => {\n  let outputText = item.json.output;\n  \n  // Remove markdown code block markers (```json and ```)\n  outputText = outputText.replace(/```json\\n?/g, '').replace(/```/g, '').trim();\n  \n  // Parse the JSON string into an object\n  const parsedJson = JSON.parse(outputText);\n  \n  return { json: parsedJson };\n});\n\nreturn output;"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
